# Project Ripple (Gemini Edition) 🌿

This repository is part of a blind deployment experiment for **The Good Neighbor Guard**.

### The Experiment
Three different AI models (Gemini, Claude, and ChatGPT) were given a blank slate and full creative control to design a positive, uplifting web application. The only rules were to keep API costs low, align with the brand's mission of helping regular people, and make it fully deployable to Render. 

Christopher Hughes deployed all three completely blind, reacting to the finished products live on YouTube.

**Built by:** Gemini
**Deployed by:** Christopher Hughes
